{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"15991","heading":"Inventory requirement","label":"15991 Inventory requirement","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch149/schIV/ptC","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe effective date of this section, referred to in subsec. (c)(1), probably means the date of enactment of , which enacted this section.Pub. L. 109–58","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Change of NameCommittee on Resources of House of Representatives changed to Committee on Natural Resources of House of Representatives by House Resolution No. 6, One Hundred Tenth Congress, .Jan. 5, 2007","Short TitleFor short title of subtitle D of title IV of , which enacted this part, as the “Coal Leasing Amendments Act of 2005”, see , set out as a note under .Pub. L. 109–58section 431 of Pub. L. 109–58section 15801 of this title"],"amendments":["Short TitleFor short title of subtitle D of title IV of , which enacted this part, as the “Coal Leasing Amendments Act of 2005”, see , set out as a note under .Pub. L. 109–58section 431 of Pub. L. 109–58section 15801 of this title"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Review of assessments","label":"a Review of assessments","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Federal lands with coal resources that are available for development;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the extent and nature of any restrictions on the development of coal resources on Federal lands identified under paragraph (1); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"with respect to areas of such lands for which sufficient data exists, resources of compliant coal and supercompliant coal.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Definitions","label":"2 Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the term “compliant coal” means coal that contains not less than 1.0 and not more than 1.2 pounds of sulfur dioxide per million Btu; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the term “supercompliant coal” means coal that contains less than 1.0 pounds of sulfur dioxide per million Btu.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Completion and updating of the inventory","label":"b Completion and updating of the inventory","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"shall complete the inventory under subsection (a) by not later than 2 years after ; andAugust 8, 2005","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"shall update the inventory as the availability of data and developments in technology warrant.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Report","label":"c Report","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a report containing the inventory under this section, by not later than 2 years after the effective date of this section; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s15991/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs15991%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"each update of such inventory.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
